SETBURNRATE

NAME
        SetBurnRate()


SYNOPSIS
        static int SetBurnRate(int x)


DESCRIPTION
        Returns the rate at which a thing burns. A higher number is a slower burn.

EXAMPLES
        To consume one unit of fuel every 5 heart beats: SetBurnRate(5)

LOCATION
        /lib/burn
/lib/lamp


SEE ALSO
        GetBurnRate


Author
        Cratylus


